 Ever since her husband s death Ayanda has been in mourning away from the spotlight.However in the wake of fellow gospel star Lundi Tyamara s death Ayanda attended his memorial service at Grace Bible Church to pay her respects.Lundi played a vital role in Sfiso s career by helping him break into the industry a gesture that has not been forgotten by his family.Dressed in all-black Ayanda struggled to fight back tears throughout the service.Earlier this week Sfiso s son Ngcweti said that Lundi s death had left Ayanda devastated. Uncle Lundi your passing has reversed our healing process especially mom he said.Lundi Tyamara will be laid to rest this Sunday following a funeral service at Zwelethemba Stadium in Worcester Western Cape.